events.name: ロパロ略奪団団員隊長
ロパロ略奪団員襲撃隊1
ロパロ略奪団員襲撃隊2

parameters:
Leader of the Loparo Plundering Squad: Damn it! What the
hell is going on!?

Leader of the Loparo Plundering Squad: And those guys...!
They fed us false information...!

Leader of the Loparo Plundering Squad: What the hell, you
guys!

Clea: We came here on General Atu's request. There's no
mistake that you're the culprits behind the carriage raid,
right?

Leader of the Loparo Plundering Squad: General Atu...!? Did
you even drag that man to Camps?

Leader of the Loparo Plundering Squad: ...Even more so, I
refuse to die in a place like this!

Leader of the Loparo Plundering Squad: General Atu, the
nobleman... and even the Ema Thief Gang showed up...
Thief Nora: Do you know about the Ema Thief Gang!?

Leader of the Loparo Plundering Squad: Those guys who spread
false information about the carriage... were the Ema Thief
Gang... hehehe.

Leader of the Loparo Plundering Squad: We've been completely
deceived.

Thief Nora: That's a lie! There's no way our leaders would
do something like that!

Leader of the Loparo Plundering Squad: Well then, if you
look at it from there, we were lured in and they cleverly
stole the cargo from the carriage.

Leader of the Loparo Plundering Squad: We might have done
well this time... but it was the Ema Thief Gang who turned
Camps upside down.

Leader of the Loparo Plundering Squad: Nobles, Imperial
Army, and even fellow professionals, we consider all of them
as enemies. The Ema Thief Gang no longer has a place to
survive in Camps.
Thief Nora: That is... Captain... Captain Clevo!!
Thief Nora: Yes... I'm relieved that everyone is safe.

Thief Nora: But the Emma Thief Guild that I know wouldn't do
something like this.

Thief Nora: That's why... ugh... if only I could hand over
the Dragon's Eye, I wouldn't have to do something like this.

Clea: Don't worry, I will definitely make sure Nora-san and
I reunite.
General Atu: So you guys were here!

General Atu: It seems you have captured the attackers! It's
nothing significant, but please accept your reward.

Priestess Sophia: Will this incident change the situation in
Camps?

General Atu: It has become an unavoidable threat that can no
longer be overlooked with sympathy.

General Atu: I am not enthusiastic about it either, but a
large-scale battle is bound to occur in Camps soon.

General Atu: Well then, I'll go. I don't want to see them,
but there's a report from Pido.

Mage Relm: Don't worry! If we can find the Emma Thief Guild
before them, everything will be fine!

Thief Nora: Yes... I will definitely find them. This time,
it's my turn to save everyone in the Emma Thief Guild.
